short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Creates a keyboard shortcut (Alt + Shift + P) to toggle the pinned state of the currently selected tab

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Homzic Extension that uses the Tab Pinning API. Enables a new keyboard shortcut (Ctrl + Shift + P) to toggle pinning and unpinning of the current tab.
